Package hu.bme.mit.theta.grammar.dsl.gen

Class DeclarationsBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.grammar.dsl.gen.DeclarationsBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
DeclarationsListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class DeclarationsBaseListener extends Object implements DeclarationsListener
This class provides an empty implementation of DeclarationsListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
